# 6. Results and Solutions

After allowing the PyTorch `Adam` optimizer to adjust the neural weights across 20 complete iterative cycles (Epochs), we froze the network's learning capability. It was then subjected to a rigorous examination against 10,268 previously unseen customer profiles. 

### Output Evaluation
```python
# python snippet: The Final Exam - Evaluation on the Test Set
model.eval() # Freezing dropout and batchnorm layers
